def df_info(df):
    print(' 10  DF')
    display(df.head(10))
    print('   DF')
    display(df.info())
    print(' df:', df.shape)
    print()
    print('  df')
    display(df.isna().sum())
    print('   df:', df.duplicated().sum())
    print()
    for col in df.columns:
        print('*** ', col + ':   ***')
        display(df[col].value_counts())
